# üïµÔ∏è Bug Bounty Recon Methodology

A structured and comprehensive recon methodology designed for bug bounty hunters to systematically gather information **during the recon phase**. This workflow focuses on **efficient data collection, organization, and analysis** to maximize effectiveness while keeping the process safe and non-intrusive.

---

## üìå Table of Contents

- [Features](#features)
- [Methodology Overview](#methodology-overview)
- [Recommended Tools & Example Commands](#recommended-tools--example-commands)
- [Contributing](#contributing)
